   * See UTKLDocDB-doc-780 for a description of this software *
   * The compilation  method from this document is outdated   *
   * Use the below instructions to compile                    *

   === Compile with cmake  ===
     $ mkdir build
     $ cd build
     $ cmake -DROOT_HOME=<ROOTSYS> ..
     $ make


   === Running ===
     (* Return back to main directory (cd .. from compile step) *)
     execute with:
     $ bin/crmt
     usage will be displayed, see document for details

   === Configuration file setting ===
     See above DocDB entry for description

   === Tested Compilers ===
     * LLVM/Clang 3.3 on OS X
     * LLVM/Clang 3.2 on Ubuntu
     * LLVM/Clang 3.0 on FreeBSD
     * GCC g++ 4.8.1 on Ubuntu
     * GCC g++ 4.8.2 on FreeBSD
